246
00:25:17,916 --> 00:25:19,975
Papá. ¡Oye, papá!

247
00:25:23,655 --> 00:25:24,781
¡Papá!

248
00:25:28,093 --> 00:25:29,117
¡Papá!

249
00:25:47,479 --> 00:25:48,673
¡Por Dios!

250
00:25:55,120 --> 00:25:57,054
